public class CTRParallelInits_SendTopAgents
extends jade.core.behaviours.ParallelBehaviour

The CTRParallelInits_SendTopAgents allows the parallel execution of several CTRInit_SendTopAgents protocols of according the number of needs. It executes its sub-behaviours (CTRInit_SendTopAgents) concurrently, and it terminates when a particular condition on its sub-behaviours is met i.e. when all them are done.
